478
00:56:19,412 --> 00:56:26,352
Pa, cujemo da i tebe ima svuda.
-Ne znam baš ništa o tome.

479
00:56:28,583 --> 00:56:33,585
Samo se zajebavam s vama.
Znate vi to.

480
00:56:35,217 --> 00:56:37,217
RD.

481
00:56:37,467 --> 00:56:40,726
