686
01:19:20,692 --> 01:19:25,586
Pojedinac mnogo sluša
o licnoj slobodi.

687
01:19:27,701 --> 01:19:34,018
Ali, kada vidite divljaštvo coveka,
i kad vas tretiraju licnim dozama,

688
01:19:41,926 --> 01:19:46,374
